description: Welcome everyone to the Tran-sending Hope dragapaoloza!!! . This benefit is for the transparent organization of Rochester. We will have a lot of amazing performers that will be performing that night This show is on November 29th. Doors will open at 9:30pm, show stars at 10pm. It’s an 18+ show with a $5 cover. A portion of the door and a portion of tips will be donated.
